{"tid":1303053,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"玩電話玩到手麻痹","createTime":"2019-07-10T07:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T12:03:58.000Z","uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5bc5992b1160012bd2602b03f4a9653b4b73f5d9","tid":1303053,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"約一年前試過半夜醒左，發現右手手指尾伸唔直，唔痛無感覺。但因為係醒左突然發現，睡前好地地唔知係因為玩電話多定自己壓到咁。<br />\n<br />\n上網查過幾乎肯定係「伸指肌腱斷裂」，症狀完全一樣，多數係尾指發生，因為條肌腱較細。之後我上淘寶買左D手指套，套住唔比佢屈曲，唔使兩個月後竟然好返，最初仲彎彎地伸唔太直，過多幾個月就可以伸到原來咁直。<br />\n<br />\n我查過原來近年電話瘋行，多左唔少人有咁既情況，以往發生最多係打籃球既人身上。<br />\n<br />\n而近來電話越買越大，成塊餅咁揸住係手，長期個姿態搞到隻手已經感到有時候痹痹地。而且唔只係揸機嗰隻手，連掃mon打字隻手都相同情況。<br />\n<br />\n再咁樂落去我覺得會有D好可怕既事發生係我身上。 但冇電話用可能會更可怕，除左戒電話仲有冇其他方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8819bebebbcb2c7d3452167555eb9acb316ae555","tid":1303053,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左戒電話仲有咩方法"},{"pid":"dbe9fbfbb15e4d5dab7c096815fae71c0b8d264c","tid":1303053,"uid":156326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"認真 試吓用念力玩電話丫"},{"pid":"6177fc31dbcc7246228e326a885b2258ca87ede5","tid":1303053,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"打飛機嘅動作 有助舒緩 玩電話帶黎嘅疲勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1323566522ae1173296dd42a55b166c51ea667d5","tid":1303053,"uid":166117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbGvyqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbGvyqe.png&h=d8147e40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYXCdqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYXCdqf.png&h=3fab917f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b74f7d11d169d99d655851793518e031a80a58","tid":1303053,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"On9 睇物理治療先啦"},{"pid":"79f358862f2535d7d9346cb7176bb601e9f70bbd","tid":1303053,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"有病去求醫"},{"pid":"7c39f90a854435e0e86ca0758460bf9a1bc00d0b","tid":1303053,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b74f7d11d169d99d655851793518e031a80a58","tid":1303053,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"On9 睇物理治療先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"應該係職業治療"},{"pid":"295186484435e960b17cfce7fc20cee803377be1","tid":1303053,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79f358862f2535d7d9346cb7176bb601e9f70bbd","tid":1303053,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"有病去求醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"睇過有D伸展動作做下，唔知有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9040b90f20a58bccb116062b5bfbcfffee898382","tid":1303053,"uid":6141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"休息幾日好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bb7a12a067c84ec2e5535ea101afaff21ddc72","tid":1303053,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"右手無名 尾指麻痺痛?"},{"pid":"29bdc57154909b75cf137cb7f4a093efcb4c54f3","tid":1303053,"uid":140283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"問下啲NBA 球星"},{"pid":"24800a49cce8d5164bf5ce570958eab6165bf227","tid":1303053,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99bb7a12a067c84ec2e5535ea101afaff21ddc72","tid":1303053,